  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://f1.ct.hjfile.cn/pic/201402/4341f034-1ba5-4083-b013-8e5b56e7ecfe.jpg\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>唐伯虎带你玩转英文口语之&ldquo;真爱&rdquo;<br />\n\t\t</strong>时间：3月11日（星期二）14:00 - 15:00<br />\n\t\t主讲老师：唐伯虎（<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/20177868/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;&gt;</a>）<br />\n\t\t公开课地点：英语活动室（<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">点击下载CCTalk</a>）</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><strong>讲师简介：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serief; line-height: 22px;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>何珩</strong></span></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serief; line-height: 22px;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">四川外语学院英语翻译学学士，英语专业八级，03年全国翻译资格三级口译译员，并具备国家二级翻译水平。拥有近10年的英语教学经验，曾先后在天津、北京、宁波等城市的知名英语培训学校担任教学主管，并定期培训外教授课。</span></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">何老师对英语教育有自己独到的见解和方法，在吸取了各地的英语教学先进理念的基础上，自创了独特的词汇学习法，能够使各个年龄层次的学员在短时间内深刻记住 并灵活运用所学到的单词，久久不忘；&ldquo;立体发音课&rdquo;，学员几次课学会所有单词的正确拼读；摒弃了传统而枯燥的语法背诵，用简单的公式和&ldquo;连锁训练&rdquo;让学员 造句信手拈来。<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/u/20177868/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">点击关注老师的沪江部落&gt;&gt;</a></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><strong>视频回顾：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><strong>课堂内容提要：</strong></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>1.Warning up&mdash;&mdash;Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n\t\t-How do you define a soul mate?<br />\n\t\t-Which is more important to you, to love or to be loved?<br />\n\t\t-Where would you choose to date your boyfriend/girlfriend? Restaurant? Park? Cinema? A football match?<br />\n\t\t-What present do you want to receive most? Does it have any special meaning?<br />\n\t\t-Do you believe in cyber love? Why/Why not?</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>2.Vocabulary</strong><br />\n\t\tforevermore<br />\n\t\tTogetherness<br />\n\t\tscatter<br />\n\t\tjoyous<br />\n\t\tlute<br />\n\t\tquiver<br />\n\t\tpillar<br />\n\t\tOak</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>3.Listening Practice and Translation</strong><br />\n\t\tThen Almitra spoke again and said,<br />\n\t\t&quot;And what of Marriage, master?&quot;<br />\n\t\tAnd he answered saying:<br />\n\t\tYou were born together, and together you shall be forevermore.<br />\n\t\tYou shall be together when the white wings of death scatter your days.<br />\n\t\tAye, you shall be together even in the silent memory of God.<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\tBut let there be spaces in your togetherness,<br />\n\t\tAnd let the winds of the heavens dance between you.<br />\n\t\tLove one another, but make not a bond of love:<br />\n\t\tLet it rather be a moving sea between the shores of your souls.<br />\n\t\tFill each other's cup but drink not from one cup.<br />\n\t\tGive one another of your bread but eat not from the same loaf.<br />\n\t\tSing and dance together and be joyous, but let each one of you be alone.<br />\n\t\t</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>4.Game Time</strong><br />\n\t\tblind date<br />\n\t\tPick a scene!<br />\n\t\t①You are in a nice Italian restaurant. It's 7 pm, and it's raining heavily outside! (Don't forget to the order)<br />\n\t\t②You have arrived at the park (late), and your date is already there. The sun is shining brightly!<br />\n\t\t③You are in a coffee shop. It's 3 in the afternoon.<br />\n\t\t④You are in the amusement park!<br />\n\t\t⑤You are in a Chinese tea house.<br />\n\t\tKey words: hobby/ sports/ TV/ movie/ music...&nbsp;</span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">想提前一周知道最精彩的公开课安排吗？那就来订阅沪江CCTalk电子报吧！<strong><a href=\"http://app.hujiang.com/mail/sub/72/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">电子报的订阅入口&gt;&gt;</a></strong></span></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(178, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">沪江网校还为大家提供了其他的活动，欢迎大家预约：<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/app/event\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>最新活动预约</strong></a></span></span></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201209/58f013100fe44857a846c5c5aef19325.gif\" style=\"width: 377px; height: 15px;\" /></strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong>请注意！参与本活动须使用沪江全新语音学习软件CCTalk，使用指南如下：</strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t1.<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bulo.hjenglish.com/n1/?source=eng2009\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">注册</span></a></strong>沪江网获得用户名（已是沪江用户的不必注册）；<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_gkkyd\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/fdac82641c98410a9fb1352dcdff5cd3.jpg\" /></a><br />\n\t\t2. 点击网址<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(7, 93, 179);\">http://class.hujiang.com/zt/cctalk/</span></a>下载CCtalk软件；<br />\n\t\t3. 软件安装结束后，输入沪江网的<b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\">用户名</span></b>和<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><b>密码</b></span>登陆CCtalk；<br />\n\t\t4. 点击下图中用红圈标注的&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\">学习中心</span></strong>&rdquo;；</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201402/e7172aae985b489bb4ca10bfb0103589.jpg\" /></p>\n\t<p style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5. 找到&ldquo;</span><font color=\"#008000\"><b>英语活动室</b></font><font color=\"#333333\">&rdquo;位置，点击进入；</font></p>